Some northern youths on the platform of the Coalition of Northern Youth Organisations for National Integration on Monday tackled Rivers State Governor, Nyesom Wike, for allegedly demolishing a mosque at the Trans-Amadi area of Port Harcourt. They claimed that the demolition was meant to score cheap political goal. Copyright PUNCH.
